snippet.title: Badland Brawl Trailer (iOS/Android)
snippet.description:
Badland Brawl is a physics-based PvP brawling insanity, taking place in the award-winning BADLAND universe. Sling your Clones, mix them together and create explosive combos!

Now available for iOS and Android in the following countries:

Finland, Norway, Sweden, Denmark, Iceland, The Netherlands, Thailand, Philippines, Vietnam, Australia, and New Zealand!

Download for iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/badland-brawl/id1301961145
Download for Android (early access): play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.frogmind.badlandbrawl

Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/badland
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/BadlandBrawl/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/badlandbrawl
